snippet.title: Apsulov: End of Gods - Official Announcement Trailer [2019]
snippet.description:
Buy this game here: 
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/960980/Apsulov_End_of_Gods/
GOG - https://www.gog.com/game/apsulov_end_of_gods

The official Announcement trailer for Apsulov: End of gods
By Angry Demon Studio

Release: 08/08 08:00am PST 2019 
http://apsulovgame.com/


In this future viking horror you awake in a sanctuary of steel and concrete, built to honor the Norse Gods, and to house an artifact, buried in the earth aeons ago.
Unveil the secrets of the mythology, the artifacts, and the realms of Yggdrasil in Apsulov: End of Gods.
